Title: Daremo Shiranai
Description: ['One of the first ', Minna no Uta, ' music videos ever created. It follows a child\'s imagination where "nobody knows" the answers to his questions such as what does a star taste like, if he throws his dad\'s hat really hard into the sky does it become a UFO, when worm wiggles around is it really wiggling into the shape of a number and calculating mathematics, etc.']
